      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The personalized gifts market is massive and growing, but existing solutions (Shutterfly, Etsy custom prints) are either generic templates or expensive, slow custom artists. Parents, grandparents, and families want deeply personal, high-quality keepsakes \u2014 family portraits, children's book illustrations, custom recipe books, memory journals \u2014 but lack the design skills or budget for truly custom work. Family Gift Studio uses AI image generation and AI-assisted content creation to produce premium-quality personalized family gifts in hours, not weeks."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Deliver personalized AI-generated family portraits, storybooks, and keepsakes at 5x lower cost than custom artists"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Create a gift ordering experience that feels premium and personal, not automated"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Build a recurring holiday and occasion calendar that drives repeat purchases"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Target gifting occasions: Christmas, Mother's Day, Father's Day, birthdays, anniversaries, new baby"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
